{
  "texts": [
    "To generate multi-granularity instructions, first, we collected tag lists with different levels of granularity from the original instructions.",
    "Then, we provided the tag lists and statements to the GPT-4 model to generate new instructions at at three other levels.",
    "We obtained 75,888 solution steps with multi-level instructions, and used them to train the Stage 1 SFT model.",
    "To generate more pairwise responses, we first used the Stage 1 SFT model to regenerate solution trees for user instructions at each granularity level.",
    "Then, we used the reward function to score these solution trees and sample pairwise responses for each solution step."
  ]
}